Libya Rebel Tells Al Arabiya ‘We Will Take’ Sirte ‘Within Hours’

-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 
2011-03-28T20:18:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/libya-rebel-tells-al-arabiya-we-will-take-sirte-within-hours-.html
Libyan rebel forces will capture
Muammar Qaddafi’s hometown of Sirte “within hours,” military
leader Abdel Fattah Younes said in an interview on Al Arabiya
television.  “We will take it,” he said. The rebels want NATO forces
to continue their aerial support of the rebels “until all of
 Libya  is free,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alaa Shahine in Cairo at 
 asalha@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 